{"tid":1766832,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大快活既問題係咪分店少同唔就腳","createTime":"2019-12-03T01:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T16:23:17.000Z","uid":89538,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"e47d1b84c1d79e49e0e41468addec0d6ced9414c","tid":1766832,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"好簡單唔講黃定藍<br />\n黨鐵出入口永遠都係大家樂美心<br />\n商場又多數大家樂m記<br />\n<br />\n大快活硬係係d細商場呀山邊 唔方便既地鋪<br />\n最好可能係沙田連城果間 但去果頭食野 多數都上多層啦<br />\n沙田居民又點會行咁遠就係食大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都有人食 但唔會夠其他連鎖打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b65f5795ab29273aad1808d8a4b02c237fb981","tid":1766832,"uid":20352,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:23:50.000Z","msg":"大快活主力做屋邨生意"},{"pid":"4eb9c867944d6eeaf80f6db4134228752dfca455","tid":1766832,"uid":82125,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:25:55.000Z","msg":"冇炒野食 ，想佢出炒粉麵飯<br />\n同埋佢d 野食真係仲差少少"},{"pid":"5627283bb7c2c2c164435d31ac2e15bc387deac3","tid":1766832,"uid":178800,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:27:30.000Z","msg":"就憑佢當年佔中後都仍然堅持無換走杜文澤 \\<br />\n就值得我地繼續支持<br />\n至於而家杜生消失左,應該係合約完左既問題<br />\n咁多年都同一個代言人,合約完左梗係搵個第二個啦,商業考慮姐<br />\n有堅持有底線有原則,但做生意就係做生意,唔係開慈善機構"},{"pid":"0630448bb2fd9101ee4124c508c10a2747217f9d","tid":1766832,"uid":42629,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"大快活早餐同一下午茶價錢平啲，可以百搭咁加嘢食飽好多"},{"pid":"1bd70136a7db835b9f8b92c054c99f029addb11e","tid":1766832,"uid":243550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"要食就幾遠都會支持嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f38344a7141f7780715443c86da8ed0a56d1738","tid":1766832,"uid":243550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0630448bb2fd9101ee4124c508c10a2747217f9d","tid":1766832,"uid":42629